        "baseRefName": "master",
        "body": "Prove additivity of `RieszContentAux`, completing the proof that it gives a `Content`.\r\n\r\nMotivation: this gives the measure related with a positive linear functional `Î›` on compactly supported continuous functions. The next step is to characterise the constructed measure as the one giving `Î›` back.\r\n\r\nIn this PR, it is assumed to be `NNReal`-linear. The main steps to prove additivity have been proposed by @kkytola [here](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/12290#issuecomment-2125859907). A different approach is taken in #12290 for `Real`-linear `Î›`.\r\n\r\n- [x] depends on: #12266 for a variation of `PartitionOfUnity`. The new contents of this PR are contained in `MeasureTheory.Integral.linearRieszMarkovKakutani` and `Topology.ContinuousMap.CompactlySupported`.\r\n",
